1. play now button e click korle (next page e jabe and a random alphabet will
appear and the same alphabet in the keyboard background color will appear
2. we have to click the same alphabet without seeing the keyboard
3. if the alphabet matches 1 score will add in the score button
4. if the alphabet does not match
decrease 1 score in the life button out of 5 and if life button spends all the score 5 to 1 the final score section will appear.
5. can still continue playing or type "escape" to resume the game.
